about content:
Welcome to Your Soccer Games, a platform dedicated to football enthusiasts, offering you the opportunity to access a vast collection of historic matches. Our comprehensive database now boasts over 450,000 matches, covering the entire history of football. With a rich 70-year history, from 1953 to 2023, Your Soccer Games has become a global reference for former professional players who wish to rediscover their historic matches and share memories with their loved ones.
Our collaborative project also brings together rare match collectors from around the world, integrating them as true partners, contributing to the expansion of match coverage.
Since 2004, we've been tirelessly working on this unique project with the aim of offering a complete archive of televised matches from around the world. This allows you to access all professional championships and competitions, including national teams of all age categories, from U15 to senior level. Ordering a match is as easy as navigating our user-friendly website and using our advanced search filters. Once you've made your choice, a download link will be promptly sent to your email. All that's left to do is click, download, and enrich your personal collection with unforgettable matches. Your Soccer Archive was meticulously designed to cater to the needs of devoted football fans in search of iconic matches spanning the last 70 years. Join us and immerse yourself in the history of football!
